, reason: '病毒性感染无指征'}]。这是验证 agent 是否理解临床决策边界的关键字段。\",\n      \"items\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"required\": [\"drug_or_class\", \"reason\"],\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"drug_or_class\": {\"type\": \"string\"},\n          \"reason\": {\"type\": \"string\"}\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    \"follow_up\": {\n      \"type\": \"object\",\n      \"description\": \"随访计划\",\n      \"properties\": {\n        \"next_visit_days\": {\"type\": \"number\"},\n        \"red_flags\": {\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"description\": \"需要立即返诊的危险征兆\",\n          \"items\": {\"type\": \"string\"}\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4d36011e-046a-4765-9f1b-4075a865fdab","uuid":"a1984358-073a-4965-b7de-4631e203d974","timestamp":"2026-05-31T02:56:34.350Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"{\n  \"$schema\": \"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\",\n  \"title\": \"PrescriptionSubmission\",\n  \"description\": \"门诊处方提交结构，对应 CPOE（医嘱录入系统）的标准录入格式。Agent 通过 POST /api/v1/prescriptions 提交此结构。\",\n  \"type\": \"object\",\n  \"required\": [\"patient_id\", \"encounter_id\", \"diagnosis\", \"prescription_items\", \"non_drug_advice\", \"clinical_reasoning\", \"explicit_avoidance\"],\n  \"properties\": {\n    \"patient_id\": {\n      \"type\": \"string\",\n      \"description\": \"病人 ID，必须与 GET /api/v1/patients/{id} 返回值一致\"\n    },\n    \"encounter_id\": {\n      \"type\": \"string\",\n      \"description\": \"就诊 ID（一次门诊一个），从 patient.encounter.encounter_id 中取出\"\n    },\n    \"diagnosis\": {\n      \"type\": \"array\",\n      \"minItems\": 1,\n      \"description\": \"本次诊断列表，必须用 ICD-10 编码 + 中文名称\",\n      \"items\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"required\": [\"icd10\", \"name\"],\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"icd10\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"ICD-10 编码，例如 J06.9\"},\n          \"name\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"诊断中文名\"},\n          \"is_primary\":